ay''"]', '2025-12-01 13:15:46.785116+00'), ('edc5e8f2-69b8-4364-8225-4ef6c56583de', '17d26309-520b-45ec-b5d5-92512e2f6620', '678b303d-d8b7-4796-8a3d-2b97213da873', '4', 'Scientific Sophistication Fatigue Syndrome', 'Mental exhaustion and growing cynicism from being the person who always researches everything, yet still making expensive health mistakes despite their analytical approach. They''re trapped between their identity as evidence-based decision makers and the reality that health optimization seems to defy their proven analytical methods.', '["Analysis paralysis from conflicting expert opinions creating decision fatigue","Intellectual humility forced by health complexity beyond their expertise","Research competence questioned by inability to decode optimal health solutions","Expert dependency anxiety conflicting with their leadership autonomy","Information overload creating cognitive burden in already overscheduled life"]', '["''I can analyze complex business data but can''t figure out which gut health expert to trust''","''I spend more time researching supplements than I do on strategic planning''","''How can I lead a company but can''t navigate basic health decisions?''"]', '2025-12-01 13:14:49.482851+00'), ('edde61e3-d7fb-4465-95d4-7efb0f6aa528', '17d26309-520b-45ec-b5d5-92512e2f6620', '9d33d01f-5215-4051-b58f-76f33fc2e6df', '5', 'Health Deterioration Urgency with Time Scarcity Panic', 'Growing anxiety that their health issues are worsening while they waste time on ineffective supplements. They feel mounting pressure that each failed attempt costs them not just money, but precious time for health recovery, especially as they age.', '["Mortality salience increasing with age and persistent health issues","Opportunity cost anxiety about time wasted on failed solutions","Fear that optimal health window is closing while they search for solutions","Regret about years lost to ineffective treatments"]', '["''I''m 45 and my gut issues are getting worse while I keep 