llacy compounding with each failed premium purchase","Expert decision-maker identity under threat from poor health ROI","Intellectual superiority complex challenged by supplement failures","Financial competence questioned by expensive health disappointments","Status anxiety about premium choices not delivering premium results"]', '["''I''ve spent $10K+ on the best supplements and feel worse than my assistant who takes drugstore vitamins''","''How can I be crushing it in business but failing at basic health optimization?''","''I research everything obsessively but keep making expensive mistakes with my health''"]', '2025-12-01 13:14:49.482851+00'), ('ef250978-79af-4af3-9f5a-fae1234fbe55', '17d26309-520b-45ec-b5d5-92512e2f6620', 'b2cbef7c-c10d-4039-a5ec-49b6d3d69b74', '8', 'Body Betrayal and Control Loss Terror', 'Terrifying sense that their own body has become an unpredictable enemy that sabotages their plans and dreams without warning. They live in constant fear of when the next flare will strike, creating learned helplessness and desperate need to regain some control over their rebellious system.', '["Unpredictable symptom flares that derail important plans or events","Loss of trust in their body''s ability to function normally","Feeling betrayed by a body they once relied upon","Hypervigilance about every physical sensation potentially signaling a flare","Desperation to find something that gives them control over their symptoms"]', '["''I never know if I''ll wake up feeling okay or if my gut will ruin my entire day''","''My body feels like it''s working against me - I can''t trust it anymore''","''I used to take my health for granted, now every meal feels like Russian roulette''"]', '2025-12-01 13:15:46.785116+00'), ('f329969d-a5fb-4faf-98e0-28354a84acc9', '17d26309-520b-45ec-b5d5-92512e2f6620', 'b0367578-4c47-4149-87f5-492db909fcf8', '8', 'Investment Justification Anxiety', 'Mounting pressure to justify their significant health spending to partners, family, and t