o embarrassing''","''I worry my brain fog during presentations makes me look incompetent to my manager''","''How can I ask for more responsibility when I can barely manage my energy levels consistently?''"]', '2025-12-01 13:18:08.278685+00'), ('f69f11de-95b4-4543-a00b-e331c77ffc0d', '17d26309-520b-45ec-b5d5-92512e2f6620', 'ba978ac4-68e6-484a-a12a-f72a43ab0f82', '3', 'Premium investment justification paralysis', 'Having been burned by expensive health products that promised practitioner-grade results but delivered mainstream outcomes, they''re trapped between knowing they need to invest in quality and terror of making another costly mistake. Each purchase decision becomes an agonizing analysis of whether the premium price reflects genuine therapeutic value.', '["Sunk cost trauma from previous expensive supplement failures","Guilt about spending family resources on unproven interventions","Fear of financial regret if the product doesn''t deliver measurable results","Anxiety about appearing fiscally irresponsible to their partner"]', '["''I''ve already spent $3,000 this year on supplements that didn''t work - how do I know this won''t be another expensive mistake?''","''My husband keeps asking why I need $200 monthly supplements when my blood work looks the same''","''I''m scared to calculate how much I''ve wasted on products that promised everything and delivered nothing''"]', '2025-12-01 13:17:04.821693+00'), ('fb001834-11c0-4882-9a48-be8556e37ebf', '17d26309-520b-45ec-b5d5-92512e2f6620', 'faf5c581-0a78-4291-a5d6-68df043f2146', '5', 'Optimization Plateau Desperation', 'After years of systematic health tracking and optimization, they''re hitting diminishing returns while their metrics stagnate or decline. This challenges their core belief that everything can be optimized through data and methodology.', '["Identity crisis when systematic approach fails","Frustration with biological complexity vs. technical systems","Fear that they''ve maximized their potential","Anxiet